sequenceDiagram
    participant User
    participant Menu as Menu Item
    participant KB as Keyboard
    participant GPUI as GPUI Action System
    participant Handler as Action Handler
    participant App as Application

    Note over User,App: Multiple Input Methods, Single Handler

    User->>Menu: Click "About"
    Menu->>GPUI: Dispatch ShowAbout action

    User->>KB: Press Cmd+Q
    KB->>GPUI: Dispatch Quit action

    GPUI->>GPUI: Look up registered handler
    GPUI->>Handler: Call show_about(&ShowAbout, cx)
    Handler->>App: Display native dialog

    GPUI->>Handler: Call quit(&Quit, cx)
    Handler->>App: cx.quit()

    Note over GPUI,Handler: Same code handles<br/>menu + keyboard
